                    It should be noted that ffmpeg (note two Fs and not three!) is real software, and part of many open source and even commercial packages. Don't just panic and remove it - if you find a three-f version, or one in a place you don't expect to find executables, run it through virustotal.<br />
<br />
Masquerading as software that almost everyone will have on their system someplace is nasty!
